      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks for that example. It seems like there's a lot of room for things to go wrong or for \"hidden\" costs to pop up that I might not see coming. Are there any specific red flags or sneaky wording I should watch out for that might hide extra liabilities? Like, what are the most common ways these clauses can be used against someone?",
